Introduction

Mimi (미미) is a South Korean singer and actress under Badahae Entertainment. She is a former member of the girl group gugudan.
On June 23, 2016, Mimi was revealed as the third member of gugudan. The group officially debuted on June 28 with their first mini album Act. 1 The Little Mermaid.

Mimi made her acting debut in 2018 through the web drama I Picked Up A Celebrity On The Street.

On December 30, 2020, Jellyfish Entertainment announced that gugudan would be disbanding on December 31 after four years together.
